# EthioShop Web Screenshots
# 
# Place your app screenshots in this directory for PWA installation prompts.
# 
# Recommended screenshots:
# - home.png (1280x720 px) - Home screen showing product listings
# - products.png (1280x720 px) - Product detail view
# - cart.png (1280x720 px) - Shopping cart screen
# - profile.png (1280x720 px) - User profile screen
#
# Tips for good screenshots:
# - Use high-resolution images (at least 1280x720)
# - Show the app in its best light with real content
# - Include Ethiopian context where appropriate
# - Ensure text is readable
# - Use consistent styling across screenshots
#
# You can capture screenshots:
# - From the running web app using browser DevTools
# - From mobile simulators/emulators
# - Using screenshot tools on real devices